column5: Joey Tier and I walked into a small lake and used a cached canoe (super comfortable and absolutely leak-proof) to chase largemouth. That's all we could find. Over 100 fish and one slab-a-rooney.              I went back last night for an evening fish and got over 25 in less than 2 hrs. Needless to say, I got my fill of largemouth bass for a while.
Those are sweet. I could fish them all day.
nice outing and fish for sure
Sometimes bass fishing is fun...this was definitely one of those times!
